“She is a bundle of love. That’s what she is.” That’s how teacher Tharina Human’s father, Riaan Botha, described her after the first day of her bail application in Vanderbijlpark on Thursday. Human, 27, Leatitia Nel, 40, and Pieter van Zyl, 50, stand accused of kidnapping Amy’Leigh de Jager outside the Kollege Laerskool on September 2 2019. For more on the story, please visit Times Select.